PART 3: SEMANTIC MODEL REFERENCE

The Sites and Costs Summary semantic model contains these tables:

CurMonData: Main data table. Contains all site details, contract info, occupancy, and expense measures. Key columns include Site and Name, City, Country Name, Region, Active/Terminated, Commercial / Housing, Term End, Arch.Obj. ID, Name of Architectural Object, Main usage type, Contract No and Name, Postal Code, RE Region / MPL, Hemisphere, State, Street. Contains current and prior year expense measures by category, PSL-specific expense measures, and occupancy data for up to 5 occupants per site.

Billing File: Cost allocation by facility and PSL. Columns: Region, Country, Facility Name, PSL Name, PSL CC, Site, Sub PSL Name. Measures: Allocated USD, Billable FT2, % of Site Cost.

Need Attention: Facilities requiring review with addresses. Columns: Active/Terminated, Arch.Obj. ID, Name of Architectural Object, City, Street, Region, Commercial / Housing, Country Name, Hemisphere, RE Region, RE Region / MPL, RE Region/MPL Group, Area Name (From CC), Country Key, Country Manager, North America Area Name, Updated Area Name.

CurMonNBV: Net Book Value by architectural object. Columns: Arch.Obj. ID, Name of Architectural Object, Street, City, State, Category, Class, CoCd, Cost Ctr, RE Object, Re Region/MPL, Site, Status, Asset Shutdown Indicator. Measures: Current Year NBV, Next Year NBV, Next 2 Years NBV, Next 3 Years NBV, Next 4 Years NBV, Total Assets, Total Acq Value, Land Acq Value, Non Land Acq Value, Prior Month NBV, Difference.

REISPO: Space and occupancy data. Columns: PSL Name, Sub PSL Name, Site, Occupant, Occupant3, MPL Site Name, Acct Assignment Object, AO Fctn Name, Actual Rate / Fixed Rate, Unit, Unit of Capacity, M2 or FT2, Hierarchy area description, Lock Reason, Error Message, Reservation Object Type, Ext. ID Reserv. Obj. Measures: FT2, M2, Capacity, Capacity in SF, Pct, Price Factor, Occupant2.

KeyMeasures: Calculated KPI measures used across all report pages.

ZFAF: Asset financial data. Columns: Region, Country, Cost Center, Company code, Project Object, Description, Key, First 3 CC, Cancel/Refund Sites, Capitalized on, Capitalized Sites. Measures: Asset Value, Assigned, AUC Total, AUC Value, AUC-in Process, Available, Budget, DownPayments, Markup, Remaining Order Plan, sub-PSL, WBS Commitments, WBS Value.

ManagersList: Management structure. Columns: Area, Country Key, Country Manager, Country Manager User ID, Country Name, Key, Region, RespPersonEmail.

TeamHierarchy: Team structure. Columns: Country Manager, Country Manager User ID, RespPersonEmail.

CurMonNBV_ColumnName: NBV display metadata. Columns: Index, NBV_DepName, NBV_Header.

FT2orM2: Unit toggle. Columns: Category, Field.

NBV_Headers: NBV parameter display. Columns: Parameter, Parameter Fields, Parameter Order.

PredictXOrg: Organization data. Columns: PersArea_Description, PX.001 Company CD, PX.Display Name, PX.Email Address, PX.Employment Status, PX.ESG-PSL, PX.ESG-SUB-PSL, PX.First Name, PX.Last name, PX.Personal Area. Measures: PX.001 Cost Center CD, PX.315 Sender cost center.

SourceFiles: Data source tracking. Columns: Date Uploaded, Name.


